When I went for my own test I learned about these changes to the assistance
program.

The low income eligibility for repair assistance has been expanded to cover
failures at test-only stations. If you fail emissions for any reason except
tampering you can apply for repair assistance. The deductable is $100 on
repair work costing up to $600.

